Vancouver Stock Exchange said Marchvolume was 479.2 mln shares, its highest monthly volume everand up from 270.1 mln in March 1986, and share value was 679.1mln dlrs, up from 381.4 mln dlrs a year ago and second only toNovember 1980's 731.4 mln dlrs.    For the first quarter, it said volume was 1.2 billionshares, the largest ever for a quarter and up 38.7 pct from ayear earlier, and share value was 1.6 billion dlrs, second onlyto 1.7 billion dlrs in the fourth quarter of 1980 and up 47 pctfrom last year's first quarter. Reuter&#3;